text: At the Los Angeles premiere of their latest film, "John Wick: Chapter 2," stars Keanu Reeves, Common and Laurence Fishburne discuss Donald Trump's travel ban and subsequent protests. (Jan. 31)
title: Keanu on Trump travel ban: ‘just terrible’
